    </div>
    <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 pt-24 border-t border-white/5">
      <div className="space-y-4">
        <div className="text-6xl mb-6">⚡</div>
        <h3 className="text-2xl font-space font-black uppercase tracking-tighter">1. Describe</h3>
        <p className="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed font-medium">Define your sonic atmosphere using neural suggestions.</p>
      </div>
      <div className="space-y-4">
        <div className="text-6xl mb-6">👁️</div>
        <h3 className="text-2xl font-space font-black uppercase tracking-tighter">2. Synthesize</h3>
        <p className="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed font-medium">Real-time PCM synthesis into hi-fidelity WAV master files.</p>
      </div>
      <div className="space-y-4">
        <div className="text-6xl mb-6">⏳</div>
        <h3 className="text-2xl font-space font-black uppercase tracking-tighter">3. Download</h3>
